<section class="py-32 md:py-48 px-6 bg-[#F9F8F6] dark:bg-[#1A1918]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 lg:gap-24 items-center">
    <!-- Left Column: The Portrait -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 relative">
      <div class="w-full aspect-[4/5] bg-[#121212] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden relative border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 shadow-2xl">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=800&h=1000&fit=crop&crop=faces"
          alt="Clark Sell"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover grayscale contrast-125 transition-all duration-700 hover:grayscale-0"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-6 font-mono text-xs bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-md px-4 py-2 rounded text-[#EBE9E4] border border-white/10 uppercase tracking-widest">
          &gt; ID_VERIFIED
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right Column: The Narrative -->
    <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center">
      <!-- Terminal Header -->
      <div class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[#121212]/50 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/50 flex items-center mb-8">
        &gt; SYS.IDENTITY // THE_ARCHITECT
      </div>

      <!-- Headline -->
      <h2 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-[1.1] text-[#121212] dark:text-[#EBE9E4] mb-8">
        I Built the Code.<br />Then I Built the Culture.
      </h2>

      <!-- Body Copy -->
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Hi, I'm Clark Sell.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        For 25 years, I engineered complex software ecosystems. I know how to build secure, scalable infrastructure. But I quickly realized that the most elegant code in the world is useless if the humans using it don't feel like they belong.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        So, I stepped out from behind the terminal. I went on to run one of the largest community conferences in the United States, studying exactly how thousands of people connect, trust, and build loyalty in the real world.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-[#121212]/70 dark:text-[#EBE9E4]/70 leading-relaxed">
        I founded re/Human because the internet is drowning in faked AI authority and rented audiences. You don't need another marketer. You need an architect who understands both the deep-tech infrastructure and the human soul.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
